---
title: Carb Smart Thai-Style Beef Salad with Mint and Peanuts
description: Indulge in a refreshing blend of tender beef, crunchy peanuts, and fresh veggies, all enhanced by the bright flavours of mint and lemongrass. With the addition of nuoc cham, this dish offers a delightful combination of textures and tastes in every bite!

Carb Smart (50 g carbohydrates or less) is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.

